{"tid":1971040,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[肯醒未]「港澳辦」同「中聯辦」違反《基本法》22條？","createTime":"2020-04-13T15:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T09:51:47.000Z","uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1f9bb9482145f58834670b2b31a48b83844fed","tid":1971040,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"有人話「港澳辦」同「中聯辦」批評香港立法會事務係「違反《基本法》22條」，咁到底係咪事實？<br />\n基本法22條：<br />\n中央人民政府所屬各部門、各省、自治區、直轄市均不得干預香港特別行政區根據本法自行管理的事務。<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔了解中國政府結構或者會想當然，認為 「港澳辦」同「中聯辦」係「部門」，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">事實呢兩個「辦公室」係屬於「國務院辦公廳」，係國務院一部份，而唔係隸屬於 26 個「國務院部門」既任何一個。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地平時講開既國務院，就係「中國中央人民政府」。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>而 22條「不得干預」既範圍，並不包括國務院本身。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幾年前就已經有爭論過「港澳辦」同「中聯辦」係咪「國務院部門」，到中國政府到今日都仲未公開講過，但我真係想問：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 我當中聯辦係「部門」，咁係咪李克強親自出黎干預，大家就係接受？<br />\n2. 大家係咪唔記得左《基本法》158/159 條？你覺得國務院出到聲，釋法結果會係乜？<br />\n3. 點解香港人仲會覺得可以用《基本法》同中國拗數？<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n搞左成年，大家倒退返去2014/15年？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ef6a1236a3917368ff36bc07dfb45c504cb613","tid":1971040,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"唔差左睇埋呢個 post ，基本法 basis<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1291237/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1291237/</a>"},{"pid":"54ed07829a772068b3af8173179d99cdafd0aca5","tid":1971040,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">基本法158條第一款：<br />\n本法的解釋權屬於全國人民代表大會常務委員會。</div></span>"},{"pid":"a440c28135a89baafffb0f647aa9aeacef7e51f9","tid":1971040,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">基本法159條第一款：<br />\n本法的修改權屬於全國人民代表大會。</span></div>"},{"pid":"a5682724115e8ff5236fc9c195ae8194f2109371","tid":1971040,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲法治已死，唔好再提法律post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n照你咁講，所有和理非抗爭其實應該收皮，兄弟爬山都唔應該各自努力，因為港共完全咩規矩都唔跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176dc47093043bcc054adc5a7c4a60062df9d230","tid":1971040,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a5682724115e8ff5236fc9c195ae8194f2109371","tid":1971040,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲法治已死，唔好再提法律post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n照你咁講，所有和理非抗爭其實應該收皮，兄弟爬山都唔應該各自努力，因為港共完全咩規矩都唔跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"1. 和理非 = 守法抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n2. 你搞清楚，我呢個 post 唔講法治已就同你講守法，就係話你聽中聯辦不受基本法22條限制。如果你真係咁中意講守法，你咪講面我上面邊忽唔係講緊法律？"},{"pid":"8b6ae3c4b2701fa42bb0042f9c3deb4a1e40c057","tid":1971040,"uid":347632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4tKX8Fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4tKX8Fa.jpg&h=d4e85e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cVDxXyw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.